Package: activecampaignr
Title: Tidy Interface to the ActiveCampaign API v3
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Peeyoosh", "Chandra", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "pc@strategyandops.co")
Description: A tidy, cached, and MCP-ready R client for the ActiveCampaign CRM
    API v3. Provides functions for deals, contacts, accounts, campaigns, tags,
    automations, and more. Features automatic pagination, rate limiting,
    incremental sync with RDS caching, and an MCP server for AI assistant
    integration via 'mcptools'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://pcstrategyandopsco.github.io/activecampaignr/,
    https://github.com/pcstrategyandopsco/activecampaignr
